Cost analysis
Total cost: $0. Groq free tier provides all LLM inference (no credit card required). All datasets are freely downloadable. Substack ChromaDB, LangGraph, sentence-transformers, RAGAS, and DeepEval are open-source. Streamlit Community Cloud provides free hosting. The only potential micro-cost: if Claude API is used for evaluation judging during development, the initial free credits (~$5) are more than sufficient. The project can run entirely on Groq without touching Anthropic's paid API.

